        devotional: 'Revelation 19 shows Jesus returning on a white horse, eyes like a flame of fire, a sharp sword from his mouth, armies of heaven behind him. On his robe and on his thigh is written one final name: KING OF KINGS AND LORD OF LORDS. Every earthly king, every president, every CEO, every dictator, every authority — bows.\n\nThat is the political claim every Christian makes whenever they pray "Jesus is Lord." There is no higher king. There is no rival authority. Caesar is not the king of kings. The election winner is not. The boss is not. The voice in your head telling you what you have to do to be valuable is not. JESUS IS.\n\nWhich "king" in your life is trying to override Him today? Be specific. The career pressure. The peer pressure. The fear of disappointing a parent. The opinion of someone whose approval has been ruling you. Today, dethrone it. Put Him back where He belongs — at the very top of the chain of authority over your life.',
